title: Old World Charm!  2-br mil Apartment Available Sept 1st.
posting_body: ['Must see to believe!', ' Cozy and charming 2-bedroom mil available now.', 'Conveniently located close to downtown Bellevue, Microsoft and to the University of Washington.', 'Like a little palace in a park-like setting!', 'Warm, welcoming, private, high-quality mother-in-law apartment available in large, beautiful, quiet and well-maintained Medina house.', 'The apartment has tall ceilings, new plush carpet, glass french doors, natural wood, elegant light fixtures and accessories; brand new gas range and other appliances; off-street parking; new washer, dryer and private patio in park-like setting.', 'New, tiled bathroom and kitchen; picture window surrounded by green trees, flowers and fruit trees.', 'Raspberries, wild strawberries and sweet native blackberries grow in the yard during the summer!', 'This is a dream come true, especially if you like gardening in your own private, pesticide-free flower garden and pea patch!', ' Large yard, perfect for growing your own organic vegetables and beautiful flowers.', 'Very quiet, safe and beautiful home and neighborhood with lots of trees, biking and amazing walking places.', 'Situated 2 minutes from highway 520; between I-405 and I-5; near many bus lines and perfect for public transportation: 6 minutes to downtown Bellevue, 12 minutes to Redmond Microsoft, 5 minutes to UW by bus; and 12 minutes to downtown Seattle by bus (shorter times by car).', 'No pets, please; minimum 6 month lease; and absolutely no smoking!', '$1900 per month + part.', 'utilities.', '  Please phone:  Linda', 'show contact info', '(no texts, please)']
